Successful completion of the Critical Career Skills - Professional Communication certification validates knowledge of key communication principles and skills that are necessary to be effective in a work environment. These core concepts include professional communication skills: effective verbal, nonverbal and listening skills; creating business deliverables; effectively delivering a message; receiving communications; and analyzing communication scenarios <br/><img src='/images/Professional Communication.png' width='500' height='500'>
